PrecisOrder PROHIBITING ENTRY ON CERTAIN LANDS in the YUKON TERRITORY (1998- No.3, LITTLE SALMON/CARMACKS FIRST NATION, Y.T.) - which prohibits the staking of mineral claims or prospecting for precious minerals on certain tracts of land in the Yukon Territory, and provides for the repeal of the Prohibition Order made by Order in Council P.C. 1996-1845.
